{"tid":842051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【時代廣場申禁令】表演者轉戰駱克道演出吸引圍觀　遭投訴阻街","createTime":"2018-09-30T04:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T07:47:34.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5059fd1a32eb0e3263b637081560bd5229b113ee","tid":842051,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1920345/org/46032d900e9b6172db4dcd50229e03c1.jpg/6PuJ7OlK6XI2sFE7UN7ubv5m59B24dO_lN70zJTe9Mw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1920345%2Forg%2F46032d900e9b6172db4dcd50229e03c1.jpg%2F6PuJ7OlK6XI2sFE7UN7ubv5m59B24dO_lN70zJTe9Mw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=438a54d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1920350/org/c82e8a89cb406ab359b6838bb856501a.jpg/sBCqW3bQDLYn5VBizwabdXk7T3kZ92i1uzkjrbs5I60?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1920350%2Forg%2Fc82e8a89cb406ab359b6838bb856501a.jpg%2FsBCqW3bQDLYn5VBizwabdXk7T3kZ92i1uzkjrbs5I60%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=0c50484e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1920377/org/3e849c1d5566f8b9b4550f35c960ff04.jpg/ztuBA4lTzQiBEm6f4SFI11ckzkW2lyYlxB1m2MQdZtg?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1920377%2Forg%2F3e849c1d5566f8b9b4550f35c960ff04.jpg%2FztuBA4lTzQiBEm6f4SFI11ckzkW2lyYlxB1m2MQdZtg%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=48c74ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣時代廣場一向有不少街頭表演者於地下公共地方唱歌，吸引大批市民圍觀。惟時代廣場近日入稟高等法院，控告表演者以及申請禁制令，禁止他們再在時代廣場範圍進行街頭表演。<br />\n<br />\n街頭表演團體The Flame 於時代廣場表演超過六年，今日（29日）傍晚轉戰駱克道行人專用區。惟晚上9時許，有警員上前表示因接獲阻街投拆，要求他們終止表演，雙方討論近15分鐘，最終達成協議，如不用擴音器可繼續表演，不會控告他們阻街，表演恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n曾在時代廣場表演六年<br />\n街頭表演團體The Flame在時代廣場表演逾六年，惟因時代廣場近日入稟法院申請禁制令，禁止表演者在廣場範圍演出。因此，The Flame今日移師至駱克道行人專用區，惟表演仍然受阻。在表演期間，約晚上9時15分有警員上前指，有人投訴阻街要求終止表演，雙方討論近15分鐘仍未解決。<br />\n<br />\n其後雙方達成協議，警員指如不使用擴音器可繼續表演，不會控告他們阻街，表演最終恢復正常。直至晚上10時，現場仍有超過40名市民和遊客圍觀，7至8名警員仍在場觀察情況。據了解，現場一名紫色上衣的中年男子於上址作出投訴阻街，今日亦有現身到場，期間與警員「密密斟」訴。至於附近東角商場及SOGO，亦有管理公司人員到現場了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n時代廣場有限公司早前入禀高等法院，控告音樂人李冠傑和其他在時代廣場表演的表演者，指他們的表演造成滋擾，要求法庭宣告街頭表演不屬於公契中所指的「靜態康樂活動」，並申請禁制令禁止他們再於時代廣場進行街頭表演。"},{"pid":"4cf5999119ba67320d36e98ee1206e6907f61712","tid":842051,"uid":144201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"我寧願睇busking都唔撚想見到啲大陸老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5fc5af79cc8a191fb55ac9db6a462e01508739","tid":842051,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"班垃圾以為度度都好似旺角無王管?<br />\n你去老銅踩住既係地產佬既地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd3530c535a82e3de29ebd1e898b363966787b5","tid":842051,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5fc5af79cc8a191fb55ac9db6a462e01508739","tid":842051,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"班垃圾以為度度都好似旺角無王管?<br />\n你去老銅踩住既係地產佬既地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"今次到大劉地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  祝君好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7af46e1b4ccb109d2460c96f90022695117982b","tid":842051,"uid":109983,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4cf5999119ba67320d36e98ee1206e6907f61712","tid":842051,"uid":144201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"我寧願睇busking都唔撚想見到啲大陸老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"咪一樣阻9住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b74418acb67236